==Dutch==
[[Category:Dutch personal pronouns]]
===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/i:/}}

===Personal pronoun===
'''ie'''

# ''Third-person singular, masculine, subjective, mute form:'' [[he]].
''hoe doet-ie dat?'', 'how does he do that?'.

====Usage notes====
Generally, this form is not used in [[Flanders]], and in the [[Netherlands]], is largely restricted to spoken language.

