==[[Esperanto]]==
===Etymology===
Esperanto ''[[i-]]'' (indeterminate [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix) + ''[[-e]]'' (correlative suffix of place)

===Correlative===
'''ie''' (''accusative'' '''[[ien]]''')

# [[somewhere]] (indeterminate correlative of place)
#: Like other indeterminate correlatives, '''ie''' can be combined with ''[[ajn]]'', the adverbial particle of generality. '''''Ie''' ajn'' thus means ''[[anywhere]]''.

